install the newest python
run pip install pipenv
cerate a new forder and open on vs code 
run pipenv install django 

run pipenv shell // to run the virtual environment
run django-admin startproject storefront . //  the storefront is the project name
run python manage.py runserver // to start the project and run on a local server 


run python manage.py startapp playground // to start a new app with the name play graound